race.comment: DARLING TAKE CARE (8) improved performance last start when she closed late for a game second over 1005m at this track. Can tag the good speed again and gets her chance. PARADING GUS (2) nice type who shouldn't be a Maiden for long. Covered plenty of ground in the run as favourite when a tiring fifth over 1200m at the Sunshine Coast. Kept up to the mark with a trial placing over 1000m at Doomben. Top three player. SPICY WINGS (1) bombed the start on debut when a plugging fourth over 1000m at Ballina. Further improved now and gets his chance from the draw. ARTIE VAINQUEUR (5) Three-year-old filly by Flying Artie from Written In Vain on debut for the Lindsay Hatch yard. Not that far away in her only trial when fifth at Toowoomba Inner Track over 650m. Keep safe,
